# Component Organization Rules

## Folder Structure

Components are organized by application and functionality:

### Shared Components (`src/components/shared/`)
- [LandingPage.tsx](mdc:src/components/shared/LandingPage.tsx) - Main landing page with app selection
- [AuthGuard.tsx](mdc:src/components/shared/AuthGuard.tsx) - Authentication protection wrapper
- [AuthModal.tsx](mdc:src/components/shared/AuthModal.tsx) - User authentication modal
- [EmailVerification.tsx](mdc:src/components/shared/EmailVerification.tsx) - Email verification component

### Time Tracker App (`src/components/time-tracker/`)
- [TimeTrackerApp.tsx](mdc:src/components/time-tracker/TimeTrackerApp.tsx) - Main time tracker application
- [Activities.tsx](mdc:src/components/time-tracker/Activities.tsx) - Activity management and history
- [Dashboard.tsx](mdc:src/components/time-tracker/Dashboard.tsx) - Analytics and insights
- [Settings.tsx](mdc:src/components/time-tracker/Settings.tsx) - User settings and categories
- [Navbar.tsx](mdc:src/components/time-tracker/Navbar.tsx) - Navigation bar
- Timer components: [TimerView.tsx](mdc:src/components/time-tracker/TimerView.tsx), [TimerControls.tsx](mdc:src/components/time-tracker/TimerControls.tsx), [TimerDisplay.tsx](mdc:src/components/time-tracker/TimerDisplay.tsx)
- Modals: [ActivityModal.tsx](mdc:src/components/time-tracker/ActivityModal.tsx), [MetadataForm.tsx](mdc:src/components/time-tracker/MetadataForm.tsx)

### Expense Tracker App (`src/components/expense-tracker/`)
- [ExpenseTracker.tsx](mdc:src/components/expense-tracker/ExpenseTracker.tsx) - Under construction page

## Organization Rules

1. **App-Specific Components**: Place components that are only used by one app in that app's folder
2. **Shared Components**: Place components used by multiple apps in the `shared/` folder
3. **Main App Components**: Each app should have a main component (e.g., `TimeTrackerApp.tsx`)
4. **Related Components**: Group related components together (e.g., timer components, modal components)
